               <p>BLAKE PENNY. I am a baker - I had put my basket down in <placeName id="t18220220-208-crimeloc1119">Portman-place</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18220220-208-crimeloc1119" type="placeName" value="Portman-place"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18220220-208-crimeloc1119" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220220-208-off1117 t18220220-208-crimeloc1119"></join>, on the 31st of January, about one o'clock, and went a short distance with two loaves - on returning, I saw a number of people, and missed four loaves. It belonged to 
               <persName id="t18220220-208-person1857">
                  Silvester 
                  Sapsworth
               <interp inst="t18220220-208-person1857" type="surname" value="Sapsworth"></interp>
